tion><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 10:23:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/bhp-expects-copper-demand-grow-by-1-mln-metric-tons-year-until-2035-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>Stellantis警告后欧洲汽车股蒸发100亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-autos-stocks-wipe-off-10-bln-after-stellantis-warning-2024-09-30/</link><description>欧洲汽车股周一下跌近 4%，此前 Stellantis、大众和阿斯顿发出的警告再次引发了人们对该行业今年因需求放缓和中国激烈竞争而受损的盈利前景的担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 10:09:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-autos-stocks-wipe-off-10-bln-after-stellantis-warning-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>Epic Games 指责三星、谷歌计划阻止应用竞争对手</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/epic-games-accuses-samsung-google-scheme-block-app-rivals-2024-09-30/</link><description>《堡垒之夜》视频游戏制造商 Epic Games 周一指责 Alphabet 旗下的谷歌和全球最大的 Android 手机制造商三星合谋保护谷歌的 Play 商店免受竞争。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 09:34:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/epic-games-accuses-samsung-google-scheme-block-app-rivals-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，即使在最终投票后，欧盟仍将继续与中国电动汽车谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-continue-china-electric-vehicle-talks-even-after-final-vote-say-sources-2024-09-30/</link><description>知情人士称，欧盟委员会已告知欧盟国家，即使在对中国电动汽车征收最终进口关税的提案进行投票后，欧盟委员会仍将继续与中国进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 08:50:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-continue-china-electric-vehicle-talks-even-after-final-vote-say-sources-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国投资者涌入股市，担心错过史诗般的反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-into-stocks-fear-missing-out-epic-rally-2024-09-30/</link><description>中国股市的动物精神又回来了，投资者在北京的政策刺激下涌入股市，并担心错过一些人认为的历史性反弹。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 07:45:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-into-stocks-fear-missing-out-epic-rally-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国“具有里程碑意义”的消费刺激计划出台后，痛苦的政策选择迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/painful-policy-choices-loom-after-chinas-monumental-consumer-stimulus-plan-2024-09-30/</link><description>中国的刺激计划旨在充实消费者的口袋，以实现2024年的增长目标，这打破了已有数十年历史的政策手册，但让家庭需求而不是投资成为发展的可持续驱动力，是一条充满艰难选择的漫长道路。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 06:34:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/painful-policy-choices-loom-after-chinas-monumental-consumer-stimulus-plan-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯顿·马丁警告供应链利润下降和中国问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/aston-martin-warns-lower-profit-supply-chain-china-woes-2024-09-30/</link><description>阿斯顿·马丁周一警告称，由于供应链中断和中国市场疲软，年度核心利润将下降，并下调了产量预期，导致股价早盘下跌 8%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 06:10:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/aston-martin-warns-lower-profit-supply-chain-china-woes-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>随着交易撮合者寻求海外增长，亚洲跨境并购复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/cross-border-ma-recovers-asia-dealmakers-look-abroad-growth-2024-09-30/</link><description>今年，亚太地区企业的跨境并购有所复苏，在日本，企业在应对利率上升的调整后寻求新的增长点，跨境并购也蓬勃发展。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 06:10:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/cross-border-ma-recovers-asia-dealmakers-look-abroad-growth-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>Stellantis以全球市场和中国竞争为由对利润发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-revises-guidance-downward-citing-performance-issues-industry-dynamics-2024-09-30/</link><description>Stellantis NV周一大幅下调了年度预期，并表示将消耗比预期更多的现金，理由是行业趋势恶化、美国业务改革成本上升以及中国在电动汽车领域的竞争。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 05:41:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-revises-guidance-downward-citing-performance-issues-industry-dynamics-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，字节跳动计划使用华为芯片训练新的人工智能模型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/bytedance-plans-new-ai-model-trained-with-huawei-chips-sources-say-2024-09-30/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，随着美国的限制措施迫使这家社交媒体巨头回国寻找芯片，TikTok 的中国母公司字节跳动计划开发一种主要使用同胞华为技术公司 (HWT.UL) 芯片训练的人工智能模型。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 05:33:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/bytedance-plans-new-ai-model-trained-with-huawei-chips-sources-say-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>刺激措施助推中国股市创2008年以来最大单日涨幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-set-best-month-nearly-decade-stimulus-cheer-2024-09-30/</link><description>周一，中国股市创下 16 年来最大单日涨幅，国内 A 股成交量创历史新高，投资者争先恐后地加入北京最新一系列刺激措施引发的强劲反弹。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 05:08:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-set-best-month-nearly-decade-stimulus-cheer-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日经指数回落，中国股市上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-30/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 04:33:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>